    <h4>Biography</h4>
    <div class='note'>
      <p>Juan is a software engineer in Intel <span class="caps">SSG</span>-<span class="caps">OTC</span>. She works on OpenGL and 2D/3D graphics/display middleware for meego-tv, including window manager, DirectFB, Xorg and mesa for TV platform. She is one of the authors of mutter-meego-tv. She had worked as an embedded software engineer, covering the development of OpenGL driver, 3D driver, 3D game, 3D desktop, 2D display and 2D-3D transition, etc.</p>
    </div>
  
  
  
  
  
      
